nl.tudelft.simulation.dsol.simulators

Interface DESSSimulatorInterface<A extends java.lang.Comparable<A>,R extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<R>,T extends SimTime<A,R,T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the absolute storage type for the simulation time, e.g. Calendar, Duration, or Double.
    R - the relative type for time storage, e.g. Long for the Calendar. For most non-calendar types, the absolute and relative types are the same.
    T - the extended type itself to be able to implement a comparator on the simulation time.
    All Superinterfaces:
    nl.tudelft.simulation.event.EventProducerInterface, java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable, SimulatorInterface<A,R,T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DESSSimulatorInterface.CalendarDouble, DESSSimulatorInterface.CalendarFloat, DESSSimulatorInterface.CalendarLong, DESSSimulatorInterface.TimeDouble, DESSSimulatorInterface.TimeDoubleUnit, DESSSimulatorInterface.TimeFloat, DESSSimulatorInterface.TimeFloatUnit, DESSSimulatorInterface.TimeLong, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface<A,R,T>, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.CalendarDouble, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.CalendarFloat, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.CalendarLong, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.TimeDouble, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.TimeDoubleUnit, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.TimeFloat, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.TimeFloatUnit, DEVDESSSimulatorInterface.TimeLong
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DESSSimulator, DESSSimulator.CalendarDouble, DESSSimulator.CalendarFloat, DESSSimulator.CalendarLong, DESSSimulator.TimeDouble, DESSSimulator.TimeDoubleUnit, DESSSimulator.TimeFloat, DESSSimulator.TimeFloatUnit, DESSSimulator.TimeLong, DEVDESSAnimator, DEVDESSAnimator.CalendarDouble, DEVDESSAnimator.CalendarFloat, DEVDESSAnimator.CalendarLong, DEVDESSAnimator.DoubleUnit, DEVDESSAnimator.TimeDouble, DEVDESSAnimator.TimeFloat, DEVDESSAnimator.TimeFloatUnit, DEVDESSAnimator.TimeLong, DEVDESSSimulator, DEVDESSSimulator.CalendarDouble, DEVDESSSimulator.CalendarFloat, DEVDESSSimulator.CalendarLong, DEVDESSSimulator.TimeDouble, DEVDESSSimulator.TimeDoubleUnit, DEVDESSSimulator.TimeFloat, DEVDESSSimulator.TimeFloatUnit, DEVDESSSimulator.TimeLong

    public interface DESSSimulatorInterface<A extends java.lang.Comparable<A>,R extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<R>,T extends SimTime<A,R,T>>
extends SimulatorInterface<A,R,T>
    The DESS defines the interface of the DESS simulator. DESS stands for the Differential Equation System Specification. More information on Modeling and Simulation can be found in "Theory of Modeling and Simulation" by Bernard Zeigler et. al.
